        "changelog": "<h4>Content Writer 1.0<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>First development version.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>Content Writer 2.0<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>First official version.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>Content Writer 2.1<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Added WP post slug to response on post create<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>Content Writer 2.2<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fixed: post date on publishing<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>Content Writer 2.3<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fixed: post status on publishing<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>Content Writer 2.4<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Added: ability to change post status from published to draft<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>Content Writer 3.0<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Added: multisite support<\/li>\n<li>Added: posting with XML-RPC WordPress API<\/li>\n<li>Added: keywords counter on edit post page<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>Content Writer 3.1<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Added: writer info keyword details refresh automatically on typing<\/li>\n<li>Added: code for updating plugin with external POST request<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>Content Writer 3.2<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fixed: timeout on get request increased to 20 sec<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>Content Writer 3.2.1<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fixed: auto update function<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>Content Writer 3.3<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Added: ability to post to WP page<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>Content Writer 3.4<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fixed: removed extra margin from <\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>&lt;<\/p>\n<p>p&gt; and  tags in WP content editor<br \/>\n* Added: real-time counting of words and keywords in post editor<\/p>\n<h4>Content Writer 3.4.1<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fixed: Improvements<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>Content Writer 3.5<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fixed: Post Encryption Added<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>Content Writer 3.5.1<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fixed: Use wordpress unzipping instead of php unzipping for updating plugin<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>Content Writer 3.5.2<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fixed: Replacing SoapClient client library<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>Content Writer 3.5.3<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fixed: Add image url to response result<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>Content Writer 3.5.4<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fixed: Fixes for Image URL<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>Content Writer 3.5.5<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fixed: PHP 7++<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>Content Writer 3.5.6<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fixed: Remove deprecated setting tab<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>Content Writer 3.5.7<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Added: Add post_url to conwr_get_post<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>Content Writer 3.5.8<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fixed: Outdated features removed<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>Content Writer 3.6<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fixed: use regular functions in &#8220;init&#8221; hook instead of WP Rest API (reason: some sites had issues with sending requests to WP Rest API)<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>Content Writer 3.6.1<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fixed: plugins update label didn&#8217;t show up in Plugins list<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>Content Writer 3.6.2<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Added: some bugs fixed<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>Content Writer 3.6.3<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fixed: update functions removed<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>Content Writer 3.6.4<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fixed: plugin verification with new users<\/li>\n<li>Added: remote plugin update feature<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>Content Writer 3.6.5<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fixed: new api url<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>Content Writer 3.6.6<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fixed: images posting<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n",
